<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Apache Lucene versions 4.10.x</li>
</ul>

<h1 class="wikiHeadline1" id="H-WhatsComingNext"><a href="/2015/05/06/hibernate-search-520-final-brings-full-multitenancy-support#H-WhatsComingNext">What's coming next?</a></h1>

<p class="wikiPara">
